{"type": "article", "id": 2221, "title": "B&O PLAY & Hard Graft 联名皮革耳机配件系列", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-07T22:56:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 2, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 4, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052222565DO0NbapuxlWJGYo.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<div>\r\n\t<span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">相信音乐发烧友们对北欧品牌 B&amp;O PLAY 的耳机不会感到陌生。日前它们联手英国人气皮革配件品牌 Hard Graft 合作推出了一系列皮革耳机配件，为 B&amp;O PLAY 旗下 H6 、Form 2i 以及 H3 三款人气耳机独身定制了 3 个专属的保护套件，除了沿用 Hard Graft 标志性的意大利优质皮革材质外，还根据耳机的造型与大小带来不同的设计，不仅能够存储，亦有悬挂、保护等功能。售价 34 至 159 欧元不等，</span><a href=\"http://www.beoplay.com/hardgraft/peak\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a><span style=\"line-height:1.5;\">。</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135101Z12bjsUQHO3q90ma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135102juGheLmPyDHYtZgq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135103OB6pF5MtoJjCbSwv.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"420\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65661642\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135103d6eV1IakPSmvx8wl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135104HdnBrMiCIF4ctSyW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}